data.description:
Beautiful modern home located in D.R. Horton Master Planned Community in Watersbend located in North Fort Worth. 1 Story 4bed 2bath 2Car with Study room. Spacious Living & Dining opens to Large Chef's Kitchen with Granite counter tops, Breakfast Bar Large private Master at rear of the home with dual sink vanity & walk-in Closet*Home is Connected Smart Home System* Covered Back Patio*Sprinkler System, Landscaping Pkg & more!*Residents enjoy a 4.5 ACRE Amenity Center with Pool, Splash Area, Playground, Softball & Soccer Field!*Easy access to I35W,287 & I820*Minutes to Shopping & Dining. 
Owner finance available option available for 5% interest.
